title: LIVE BLOG: Rangers defeat Blue Jays in extra innings
text:
The Toronto Blue Jays will send Marcus Stroman to the mound as they look to even their series with the Texas Rangers at one game apiece.
Follow our live blog for all the latest details from a sold-out Rogers Centre.
